{
  "stem": "2916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She couldn't put her dress on fast enough, so this tall, beefy SS woman was twisting her arm, and she was shrieking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I noticed that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when I noticed that, I see it's my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She is going to break the arm of my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I jumped on her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I jump on her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know what that means to jump on an SS woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I jumped on her and screamed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, you are going to break her arm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she started to kick me and beat me with her whip.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I fell down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for a short while, I lost consciousness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she didn't kill me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She just beat me very badly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very badly bruised, but she didn't kill me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so everybody was already out of the showers when my mother managed to bring me back, and called, Elli, wake up, wake up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I came to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went on the appel, and we were taken onto the trains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we survived Auschwitz, and we were away from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were taken to Germany westward to a place which is in Bavaria called Augsburg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a factory town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were put you in a factory compound, not a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the SS people who were awaiting us at the train were very surprised to see who came.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said to our leader-- there was one woman who was our spokeswoman-- they said we asked for 500 women, not for men.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we said, but we are women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were shaven again, freshly shaven, and we were by now stick-like, so we didn't have any shape, and we looked like men.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, then they told us, where is your luggage?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody started laughing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Luggage?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
